{"tid":993823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首演國產科幻片  達哥演「科幻型男」","createTime":"2019-01-24T08:20:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T04:21:46.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef2523c865dd06db33346bb59f7742abd722bc3","tid":993823,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:20:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190124/_2019012415512592767.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190124%2F_2019012415512592767.jpg&h=457359a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《流浪地球》是改編自劉慈欣所著同名小說的中國科幻電影，由郭帆執導，將於2019年2月5日(農曆大年初一)上映。領銜主演包括屈楚蕭、李光潔、吳孟達、趙今麥；主演包括屈菁菁、張亦馳、楊皓宇、李虹辰、楊軼、姜志剛、張歡及吳京。<br />\n<br />\n而其中最為大家注目的就是吳孟達，今次他將會化身「科幻型男」，不少網民都對他的造形海報大讚，「科幻」配「吳孟達」完全毫無違和感。65歲的他是人生中第一次演科幻片，他的角色是「國民姥爺」，他說：「我在片中飾演的是朵朵和劉啟的姥爺，他很寵愛孫子孫女，雖然這兩個孩子特別淘氣，不讓人省心，但是他為了讓孩子們能夠在惡劣的環境中感受到『家』的情感，付出了自己的全部。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190124/_2019012415512477263.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190124%2F_2019012415512477263.jpg&h=62e03ac6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小說《流浪地球》是中國當代科幻作家劉慈欣在2000年完成的作品，講述了在未來，太陽即將毀滅，人類在地球表面建造出巨大的推進器，尋找新家園。然而宇宙之路危機四伏，為了拯救地球，為了人類能在漫長的2500年後抵達新的家園，流浪地球時代的年輕人挺身而出，展開爭分奪秒的生死之戰。小說曾獲得科幻小說銀河獎特等獎，其作品成功地將極端的空靈和厚重的現實結合起來，極具中國特色的科幻文學風格。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190124/_2019012415512518545.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190124%2F_2019012415512518545.jpg&h=c9f6881d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1418382/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1418382%2F&d=tV9qdyV9zZdslbmYcqdCeKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=adc423fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1418382%2F&h=ddd56a02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1418382/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jsLagAjYGX0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjsLagAjYGX0&d=tV9qdyV9zZdslbmYcqdCeKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=5e9f28f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jsLagAjYGX0</a>"},{"pid":"72e4e88dfa1ef8e04c9f655f8fde6ca4772b91e7","tid":993823,"uid":23468,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:23:09.000Z","msg":"屌 以為蔡思達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eee12890c54cb55f39f9e7cfb6703570aa8d4ad","tid":993823,"uid":20867,"like":27,"dislike":18,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"72e4e88dfa1ef8e04c9f655f8fde6ca4772b91e7","tid":993823,"uid":23468,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:23:09.000Z","msg":"屌 以為蔡思達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:29:02.000Z","msg":"舊香港人：達叔<br />\n新香港人：達哥"},{"pid":"9b0688996dbfbb0fc206f8ae2e3e28f2dbc54c08","tid":993823,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":15,"score":-13,"quote":{"pid":"6eee12890c54cb55f39f9e7cfb6703570aa8d4ad","tid":993823,"uid":20867,"like":27,"dislike":18,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"72e4e88dfa1ef8e04c9f655f8fde6ca4772b91e7","tid":993823,"uid":23468,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:23:09.000Z","msg":"屌 以為蔡思達<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:29:02.000Z","msg":"舊香港人：達叔<br />\n新香港人：達哥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:29:58.000Z","msg":"新你老母"},{"pid":"df8eb3e8ef8b02f1ad1bfffb83319b54883b94ee","tid":993823,"uid":209487,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:33:09.000Z","msg":"